data.description: Welcome to The Landings at Glenross- A golf course community!  Enjoy the panoramic  views of holes 3 and 7 from the large/welcoming front porch.  Generous sized great room w/vaulted ceiling and lots of windows. The galley style kitchen boasts granite counters, SS appliances and wood flooring. The first floor Primary suite offers oversized bedroom, walk-in closet,  dual sinks, linen closet, gorgeous tile work throughout the oversized standing shower w/bench.  Laundry room offers upper cabinets and laundry sink. Second floor offers open concept loft, Jack-n-Jill full bathroom and 2 additional bedrooms w/ walk-in closets. Oversized 2 car garage  offers abundant storage. Community offers pool, clubhouse.This condo is move in ready and FHA approved.
